OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FVoters in Greater Manchester will go
OL,8,Fto the polls in July to vote for who
OL,9,Fthey think should be the region's
OL,10,Fmayor.
OL,12,FResidents of all 10 boroughs in
OL,13,FGreater Manchester will cast their
OL,14,Fvotes on 30 July - with the successful
OL,15,Fcandidate expected to be announced a
OL,16,Fday later.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
