OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FThe vote was triggered after Andy
OL,8,FBurnham returned to Westminster after
OL,9,Fwinner a by-election in the Makerfield
OL,10,Fconstituency, with rules stating the
OL,11,Fmayor cannot be a sitting MP.
OL,13,FThere are currently six candidates
OL,14,Fdeclared to stand - with a new voting
OL,15,Fsystem in place.
OL,17,FWhat is the voting system?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
