OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FThe first-past-the-post system will be
OL,8,Fswapped for the supplementary vote -
OL,9,Fin line with other mayoral elections
OL,10,Faround the country - where voters will
OL,11,Fcast a first and second choice.
OL,13,FIf one candidate is the first choice
OL,14,Ffor more than half of voters, they win
OL,15,Fimmediately.
OL,17,FIf no candidate wins more than half of
OL,18,Fthe votes, the top two candidates
OL,19,Fremain in the running, and second
OL,20,Fpreference votes for the eliminated
OL,21,Fcandidates are counted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
