OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FThe successful candidate will hold
OL,8,Foffice until the next scheduled
OL,9,Felection for the mayoralty in May 2028.
OL,11,FWho is on the ballot paper?
OL,13,FSian Astley - Reform UK
OL,15,FReform UK have announced Sian Astley,
OL,16,Felected councillor for Baguley,
OL,17,FWythenshawe, as the party's candidate.
OL,19,FMs Astley currently lives in
OL,20,FFallowfield, where she runs a design
OL,21,Fand property business.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
