OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FShe said: "Politics needs real people
OL,8,Fwith real life experience. People like
OL,9,Fme."
OL,11,FGeraldine Coggins - The Green Party
OL,13,FGeraldine Coggins, councillor for
OL,14,FAltrincham since 2018, is the Green
OL,15,FParty's candidate.
OL,17,FLooking to build on their success in
OL,18,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election,
OL,19,FCllr Coggins believes it is a straight
OL,20,Fcontest between the Greens and Nigel
OL,21,FFarage's party, Reform.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
