OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FShe said: "To make sure that we
OL,8,Ftackling the massive inequality in our
OL,9,Fcities, to be standing up for all the
OL,10,Fdifferent communities, for the people
OL,11,Fin the centre, for the people at the
OL,12,Fedges and for all the different people
OL,13,Fhere."
OL,15,FBev Craig - Labour
OL,17,FThe leader of Manchester City Council
OL,18,FBev Craig is Labour's candidate in the
OL,19,Fupcoming election.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
