OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FCouncillor Craig became the first
OL,8,Ffemale leader of the city council in
OL,9,F2021 and is its first LGBT leader.
OL,11,FLabour described her as a "former
OL,12,Fcouncil estate kid whose family
OL,13,Fendured unemployment, ill health, and
OL,14,Ffinancial hardship."
OL,16,FCllr Craig said Greater Manchester
OL,17,Ftransformed her life after moving to
OL,18,Fthe city region when she was 18.
OL,20,FPhil Eckersley - Conservatives
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
