OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FThe Conservative Party have announced
OL,8,FTrafford councillor Phil Eckersley as
OL,9,Fits candidate.
OL,11,FHe represents Bowdon Ward on Trafford
OL,12,FCouncil, where he serves as deputy
OL,13,Fleader of the Trafford Conservative
OL,14,FGroup.
OL,16,FHe said: "The Conservative Party has a
OL,17,Fclear vision for Greater Manchester,
OL,18,Fsafer streets, better transport,
OL,19,Fthriving local businesses, responsible
OL,20,Fdevelopment and value for taxpayers'
OL,21,Fmoney."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
