OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FRichard Kilpatrick - Liberal Democrats
OL,9,FFormer teacher Richard Kilpatrick, who
OL,10,Fserved as a councillor in Didsbury
OL,11,FWest for the past eight years, is the
OL,12,FLiberal Democrats' candidate.
OL,14,FHe said: "Our region has so much
OL,15,Fpotential but voters have been let
OL,16,Fdown by Labour's complacency, whilst
OL,17,Fall Reform offer is division."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
