OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FHe wants to see more investment in
OL,8,Fsocial care, more affordable public
OL,9,Ftransport, and improvements to
OL,10,Fcommunity policing.
OL,12,FMarlon West - Restore Britain
OL,14,FFormer mental health nurse Marlon West
OL,15,Fis Restore Britain's candidate for the
OL,16,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
