OL,3,CGreater Manchester mayoral election:
OL,4,CWhat you need to know and who is
OL,5,Crunning
OL,7,FWith West as mayor, Restore said it
OL,8,Fplans to attract business investment,
OL,9,Fcut wasteful spending, including
OL,10,Fwithin Greater Manchester's Combined
OL,11,FAuthority, protect greenfield, and
OL,12,Foverhaul the transport network.
OL,14,FHe said: "I have lived and worked in
OL,15,Fthis city for my entire life. I have
OL,16,Fseen what good public services look
OL,17,Flike and I have seen what happens when
OL,18,Finstitutions fail the people they are
OL,19,Fsupposed to protect."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
